dc_title_s: Map of property and land grants of the Island Heights Association on the north bank of Toms River in Ocean County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: This map depicts property and land grants of the Island Heights Association on the north bank of Toms River. The lots are divided up into 44 block sections. This map is a block print and hand ink on paper-covered linen in poor condition.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|The map survey appears to date from 1878 while the map includes updated information about land grants made in the early twentieth century.
